title: Install Direnv Using Home-Manager
tags: @zettel _method nix direnv
roam-id: c57d503e-ca42-48e4-b02c-0866135985b9
type: text/markdown

``` nix
# save this as shell.nix
programs = {
    direnv = {
      enable = true;
      enableBashIntegration = true; # see note on other shells below
      nix-direnv.enable = true;
    };

    bash.enable = true; # see note on other shells below
  };
```
